00:16:40.270 --> 00:16:41.000
Oh tidak.

00:16:42.360 --> 00:16:43.220
Sebenarnya apa?

00:16:43.910 --> 00:16:45.110
Tentang perkara ini...

00:16:46.510 --> 00:16:47.970
Apa yang anda cuba katakan?

00:16:50.670 --> 00:16:52.030
Anda benar-benar berlagak.

00:16:52.030 --> 00:16:53.630
Anda tidak masuk akal.

